# Product
AI-powered carousel generator organized by Projects.

Users:
Project → Input → AI slides → Templates render → Export.

# Stack
- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Supabase (Auth + DB + Storage)
- pnpm

Do not change stack.

# Architecture
Backend logic must be reusable by future mobile apps.

Rules:
- Business logic must live server-side.
- Avoid UI-only logic.
- Data access via server helpers.
- Prepare for API exposure later.

# Templates
Templates are stored in database, not code.

Template defines:
- layout type
- text zones
- overlays
- safe areas
- fonts
- default styles

AI never designs templates.

# AI output
AI generates structured slide JSON.
Slides validated before saving.

# UI principles
- Creator-first workflow
- Fast generation
- Minimal clicks
- Editor must be quick, not complex

# Coding rules
- Strict TypeScript
- No unnecessary dependencies
- Reusable components
- Incremental changes only
